comments.body: It is curious how the original file is inconsistent on using the `tflite::` namespace. The top of the file has `using namespace tflite;` so my inclination would be either remove that line and use `tflite::` explicitly, or remove the `tflite::` throughout and leave the `using` statement. So, if you prefer to keep the `tflite::` throughout, please remove the `using namespace tflite;` statement on line 31.
I agree! I've removed the `using` statement now.
